cloudflare-ip-updater (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Multi-record and multi-domain support (RECORD=domain:name:type)
  * IPv6 (AAAA) record support with dedicated IPv6 IP check services
  * Retry logic with exponential backoff for transient failures
  * Rate limit handling (429 responses with Retry-After)
  * Dry-run mode (--dry-run) to test without making changes
  * Configurable check interval (CHECK_INTERVAL + --setup-timer)
  * Optional DNS propagation verification (VERIFY_DNS=1)

 -- Jory A. Pratt, W5GLE <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Feb 2026 08:33:42 -0600

cloudflare-ip-updater (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Monitors external IP every 3 hours
  * Automatically updates Cloudflare DNS when IP changes
  * Systemd service and timer integration
  * Configuration via /etc/cloudflare-ip-updater/config
  * Auto-detects Zone ID and DNS Record ID if not provided

 -- Jory A. Pratt, W5GLE <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Sat, 10 Jan 2026 10:10:36 -0600